    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis amen. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/7">Otto</persName> divina favente
                        clementia Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> semper augustus.
                        Si locis divino cultui mancipatis proprietates et legum instituta augere
                        defendere et confirmare studuerimus, id non solum humana laude predicandum,
                        verum etiam divina remuneratione nobis recompensandum credimus et vere
                        scimus. Quapropter agnoscant omnes fideles nostri presentes atque futuri,
                        qualiter nos pro dei omnipotentis amore animaeque nostre absolutione nec non
                        interventu et petitione domini <persName key="#Archbishops"
                            ref="#people/4325">Leonis</persName>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Offersio/donatio #Cities #Rivers #Massae #Penalty #Castle #Tower #Ports #Comitatus #Dioecesis #Teloneum #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Districtio #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1471">sanctae <placeName key="#Teloneum #Mints"
                                ref="#places/594">Rauennatis</placeName> ecclesiae</orgName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs> suae sanctae sedi per
                        hanc nostram preceptalem paginam, sicut iam antea fecimus, confirmamus et
                        firmissime corroboramus omnes illi pertinentes episcopatus <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasteria</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesias</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitates</rs> et <rs key="#Castle">castella</rs> ac omnes
                        res quae unquam per <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">chartas antiquas
                            privilegia</rs> atque precepta ad eandem sacrosanctam Rauennatem
                        ecclesiam pertinuerunt, insuper ea quae in nostri diadematis temporibus vel
                        antea a <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1532">Iohanne</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papa</rs> ad ipsam ecclesiam sunt oblata et perpetualiter
                        donata et a nobis confirmata, videlicet <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatum</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1478"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                >Ferretranum</placeName></geogName> cum episcopatu suo et cum
                        monasterio <orgName key="#Monasteries">sancti Salvatoris</orgName> in ipso
                        comitatu posito, comitatum <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/1890"
                                ><geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1479"
                                >Cesenatensem</geogName></placeName> cum castro vetere et novo ac
                            <rs key="#Tower">turribus</rs> et omnibus sibi pertinentibus, comitatum
                            <placeName key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/4667"><geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/3913"
                                    ><orgName key="#Dioecesis"
                            >Ficoclensem</orgName></geogName></placeName> cum episcopatu suo et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">ripa</rs>, episcopatum
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/108">Rhegiensem</orgName> cum dono et
                        consecratione, sicut ipsi ecclesiae per preceptum nostrum dedimus et
                        tradidimus, simulque comitatum <placeName key="#Comitatus"><geogName
                                key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/3987"
                            >Decemanum</geogName></placeName>, [comitatum <placeName
                            key="#Comitatus"><geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/3988"
                                >Trauersarie</geogName></placeName>], comitatum <placeName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3512"><geogName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/2409">Imolensem</geogName></placeName>, comitatum
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fisheries #Comitatus #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/485"><geogName
                                key="#Fisheries #Comitatus #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#estates/2449">Comaclensem</geogName></placeName> cum ripa et
                            <rs key="#Fisheries">piscariis</rs> suis, [comitatum <placeName
                            key="#Fisheries #Comitatus #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/80"><geogName
                                key="#Fisheries #Comitatus #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#estates/84">Ferrarie</geogName></placeName> cum ripa et
                        piscariis suis] nec non districtum Rauennae cum portis ripa et portubus
                        muris publicaliis omnibus <rs key="#Teloneum">teloneis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Mints">moneta</rs> et omnem potestatem in omnibus infra et extra
                        civitatem Rauennae, <rs key="#Massae">massam</rs> quae vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Massae" ref="#estates/2479"><placeName ref="#places/4600"
                                >Fiscalia</placeName></geogName> cum <placeName ref="#places/3520"
                            >Corna ceruina</placeName>, monasterium <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">sanctae Mariae in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposa</placeName></orgName>, monasterium
                            <orgName key="#Monasteries">sancti Hilarii in Gallicata</orgName> cum
                        omni districtu placitoque suo, <rs key="#Ports">portum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fisheries #Ports"><geogName key="#Fisheries #Ports"
                                ref="#estates/2457 #estates/2465">Volanae</geogName></placeName> cum
                        piscariis suis usque ad portum Ceruiam, monasterium <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries">sancti Thomae apostoli</orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3668">sanctae
                            Euphemiae</orgName> infra civitatem <placeName ref="#places/1806"
                            >Ariminensem</placeName> cum omnibus pertinentiis eorum seu omnes res
                        quas <persName key="#Deacons"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> filius <persName key="#Marquis/duke"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> ducis per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam donationis</rs> in sanctam Rauennatem
                        ecclesiam tradidit, et quascunque <persName key="#Countess"><name
                                ref="Ingelrada">Ingelrada</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs> detinuit, sicut <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/173">avus noster</persName> in placito
                            <persName key="#Archbishops"><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName>
                        Rauennati archiepiscopo legaliter investivit itemque res et possessiones
                        quas <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lambertus</name></persName> cum uxore
                        et filiis suis habuit a mari usque ad Alpes, a fluvio <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/3548">Rheno</placeName> usque ad <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4609">Foliam</placeName>, sicut nos prefatae
                        ecclesiae olim tradidimus, insuper addimus et concedimus eidem sanctae
                        Rauennatum ecclesiae comitatum <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/3618"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                            >Bobiensem</placeName></geogName>, comitatum <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2459"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3515"
                                >Foroliuiensem</placeName></geogName>, comitatum <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2480"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/4602">Foropompiliensem</placeName></geogName> cum
                        civitatibus atque districtu earum et omnibus ad eosdem pertinentibus, sicut
                            <persName key="#Archbishops" ref="#people/177">Gilberto</persName> antea
                        eiusdem sanctae Rauennatis archiepiscopo et nunc apostolicae sedis pontifici
                        constituto diebus vitae suae tantummodo largiti sumus, quia inimici rei
                        publicae et sanctae Rauennati ecclesiae aperte facti sunt -- atque hec omnia
                        in omnibus, sicut iam confirmavimus et olim confirmata fuerunt, prefato
                        Leoni archiepiscopo et suis successoribus stabilimus. Unde imperiali
                        statuimus edicto ut, si aliquis dux marchio comes vicecomes seu ulla imperii
                        nostri magna parvaque persona eandem Rauennatem ecclesiam de omnibus
                        predictis molestare inquietare aut disvestire tentaverit, <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >mille libras auri optimi</rs> compositurum se sapiat, medietatem <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">camerae nostrae</rs> et medietatem <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">prescripto archiepiscopo</rs>
                        suisque successoribus. Quod ut verius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus
                        observetur, hanc paginam propriis manibus roborantes sigilli nostri
                        impressione inferius insigniri precepimus. Signum domni Ottonis invictissimi
                        imperatoris augusti. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Eribertus"
                                >Herembertus</name></persName> cancellarius vice <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petri</name></persName> episcopi et archicancellarii recognovit. Data
                        XIIII. calen. ianuarii anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXCIX, indictione
                        XIII, anno vero Ottonis III. regnantis XVI, imperii IV; actum Rauenne;
                        feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
